{% extends "base.jinja" %}

{% block title %}Welcome - Study Session 1{% endblock %}

{% block additional_styles %}
.start-btn {
    background: #00883A;
    color: white;
    padding: 12px 30px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-size: 1.1em;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 20px;
}
.start-btn:hover {
    background: #006B2E;
}
.welcome-card {
    text-align: left;
}
.welcome-card h1 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}
.participant-highlight {
    color: #00883A;
    font-weight: bold;
}
.welcome-card h3 {
    color: #333;
    margin-top: 25px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}
.welcome-card ol {
    margin: 10px 0 15px 20px;
    padding-left: 0;
}
.welcome-card li {
    margin-bottom: 5px;
}
.welcome-card .start-btn {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 30px auto 0 auto;
    width: fit-content;
}
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<div class="welcome-card">
    <h1>Welcome <span class="participant-highlight">{{ participant_id }}</span>!</h1>
    
    <p>Thank you for joining our study on coding with AI! 
    This is a two-stage study in which you will be asked to complete a typical coding task supported by AI tools.</p>

    <h3>Study overview</h3>
    <p>In this study, you'll complete two coding sessions spaced one week apart. 
    The coding task for each session will be different, but the format stays the same across the two stages.</p>

    <p><strong>Stage 1 (today):</strong></p>
    <ol>
        <li>Background survey about your (AI) programming experience</li>
        <li>Introduction to the development environment and available AI tools</li>
        <li>Coding task to complete with the help of AI</li>
        <li>Post coding survey about your experience</li>
    </ol>

    <p><strong>Stage 2 (next week):</strong></p>
    <ol>
        <li>Additional coding task to complete with the help of AI</li>
        <li>Post coding survey about your experience</li>
    </ol>

    <p>Each stage takes about <strong>45-60 minutes</strong> to complete.</p>

    <p>During the session, your screen will be recorded. 
    We will also log your code, AI interactions, and questionnaire responses. 
    All data is anonymous, confidential, and used only for academic research.</p>

    <!-- <p><i><strong>Note:</strong> You will receive compensation only after completing both stages of the study.</i></p> -->

    <p>When you're ready, click "Start Study" to begin with your session.</p>

    <a href="/consent" class="start-btn">Start Study â†’</a>
</div>
{% endblock %}
